{"tid":1382940,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（唔想輸就入黎）擔心大家會好心壞事  千其唔可以接受利益","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:00:35.000Z","uid":121655,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"06e727193fa4fac2a1dbe48ce3d82e544d2d4bcf","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"其實出發點係好 集思廣益<br />\n如果收左你同黑警收支票有咩分別！<br />\n社會上面 有唔同聲音 比人話有金主之類<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">件事情一直都無大台 無領袖 <br />\n政府 甚至中央都好想捉個代表出黎</span><br />\n為左用得其所 唔比不法之徒 希望大家比多d意見<br />\n如果叫大家買野食去物資站拎？（或者一個地點）<br />\n又或者係一個地點 即時報個到有野食拎 <br />\n又或者可以找一些幫助（弱勢社群）既機構<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">比人影相煲大件事都唔好 心知被捕都唔好</span>"},{"pid":"02fc586c6177d78a274bf7942d3ccfe02f633c03","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"同意請推！"},{"pid":"d16aacc1243adc70c7b96c6fc4e6ce9daf731a9a","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e886c166c60ce7e2d79c300a2dff551cb6e08223","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"2472bb61b0f52ff2a203a993653cb7a42129b63f","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"11fd9865fba8b05deebe08bb5940b113c718bb6a","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7bece050a86227beff45590c00b6dd7d8433039e","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"c7b31f09673478bc88b611fb900910c6e91cd9a3","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"f156435506d104073a495d7a44f622b056d5c344","tid":1382940,"uid":121655,"like":0,